  <brief_title>A Study to Evaluate SAGE-547 in Patients With Severe Postpartum Depression</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multicenter, Randomized, Double-Blind, Parallel-Group, Placebo-Controlled Study Evaluating The Efficacy, Safety, And Pharmacokinetics Of SAGE-547 Injection In The Treatment Of Adult Female Subjects With Severe Postpartum Depression</official_title>
  <sponsors>
