  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a multicenter, randomized, double-blind, parallel-group, placebo-controlled study of
      the efficacy, safety, and pharmacokinetics of SAGE-547 Injection in adult female subjects
      diagnosed with severe postpartum depression
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
